You have to do login just once and reuse the session details received in response for accessing the other featured of the SDK, the Session and Reference_id can be saved in preference and be reused, this details would not expired until you login or change the password on this particular device, and are unique for every device.
You can use the option available on the screen for Gateway connection concurrently while setting up the transaction data, this will speeden up the over all latency of transaction process throughout.

If the AutoConnect is set to true the device has already connected it would call checkCard, if not it will first initiated the connection by calling startSerial and if the checkCardAfterConnection is set to true(through initiateWisepadConnection) then the SDK will call up checkCard internally.
